
This code base can be used as a general purpose workflow in any spring project.

Steps to use it in your project:
1. Clone the code base.
2. Remove Application.java as it is used for booting spring.
3. Create custom stage class by extending WorkFlowStage.
4. Use work flow execution engine to run with retry.

Steps to build jar out of source code:
1. Run gradle clean fatjar.
2. Jar will be created in build/libs of project folder.

